OL,3,CWorkington man jailed following
OL,4,Crobbery of a newsagent
OL,6,FA Workington man has been jailed for
OL,7,Ffour years for robbing a newsagent
OL,8,Fwith a hammer.
OL,10,FRyan Langcake, 35, of Northside,
OL,11,FWorkington robbed the store in the
OL,12,FStation Road area on 1 November 2025.
OL,14,FCCTV footage shows Langcake jumping
OL,15,Fover the counter, pushing the till
OL,16,Fonto the floor and hitting it with a
OL,17,Fhammer in an attempt to open it.
OL,19,FHe then took between #200 and #300
OL,20,Ffrom a tub behind the counter.
