OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778367989
OL,3,CWorkington man jailed following
OL,4,Crobbery of a newsagent
OL,6,FSpeaking on the case Detective
OL,7,FSergeant Peter Schofield said:
OL,8,F"Robbery is a serious offence and will
OL,9,Fnot be tolerated in Cumbria. This
OL,10,Findividual made deliberate efforts to
OL,11,Favoid being identified, but our
OL,12,Fofficers were able to track his
OL,13,Fmovements and secure the evidence
OL,14,Fneeded to bring them before the courts.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank the witnesses
OL,17,Fwho came forward, as well as the
OL,18,Fofficers involved, whose work has
OL,19,Fresulted in this offender being
OL,20,Fbrought to justice.
